PrimeNG shows that when:
	‚Ä¢	options.length === 0
	‚Ä¢	OR rendering crashed before population

Because the error occurred during .map(), Angular never reached assignment.

After this fix:
‚úî Dropdown WILL show 2 employees under h59604

